# docs/Examples.pdf build scaffolding. Tracked: gen.sh (the generator) + its
# 4 static input assets (*.desc / *-spec.json) + the helper scripts that
# produced them. Everything else here is a build artifact or scratch and is
# regenerated by `bash gen.sh > Examples.md` then the pandoc command in gen.sh's
# header. Run with mnemonic 0.55.3 (+ mnemonic-depth2 for Appendix B); the
# committed deliverable is ../docs/Examples.pdf.

# Build outputs (regenerated)
Examples.md
Examples.pdf
preamble.tex
*.err
work/

# Unused scratch (NOT read by gen.sh — it derives keys live + emits sections
# inline; these are earlier drafts / intermediate captures)
keys.env
*.out
H.txt
Hp.txt
knew.txt
section5.md
section6.md
section6_5.md
degrade.desc
degrade-spec.json
ex3.json
t_nums.desc
t_real.desc
tr2-bundle.json
